Clear- sunny- 55 degree air- 58 degree water temperature- and poplar blossom on surface of lake.
Weather clear to partly cloudy- slight chop on the water- and the temperature is 60 degrees.
Weather clear- lake very choppy- wind out of the northwest- and the lake temperature is 61 degrees.
Storms all week- windy- and some weed seed apparent on lake.
Stormy weather and cool.  No water color given.
Water temperature down 15' is 59 degrees and the weather is cool.
Weather partly cloudy- very windy- milfoil weeds up to top of water in places- and water temperature is 64 degrees.
Weather clear- sunny- no wind- 70 degrees- lake in bloom- and perch fishing is terrific.
Weather cool- some weed problem- and water temperature is 60 degrees at surface.  Weather cloudy- stormy- waves on lake- wind from northwest- air temperature is 40 degrees- can winter be far away
Water color brown- slight chop on water- sun shining- 72 degree air temperature- and 52 degrees water temperature at 10' depth.
Weeds to top of water in spots- water temperature is 50 degrees (top and bottom) - clear weather- and the air temperature is 58 degrees.  Water level down 8-10"
Weather cloudy. showers. slight chop on the lake. need the rain.
Weather clear.  Sun shining. slight breeze. somewhat cool - 42 F.
Waves quite severe- but sun shining + warm. lots of bloom in lake. 2 jet skis + 1 skier on lake.
Bad storm passed over lake at 5: 30 am.  Lots of damage at club. eagle nest blew down.
Lots of bloom in lake. many weeds floating on top of water - mostly elodea. clear sky + warm.
Weather hot - 91 F. bright sun- lots of weeds floating - elodea.
Bright sun - 20 F at 5: 00 am. 50 F at noon. leaves down. fall is here.
Cloudy and cool. 39 degrees F. water temp 47 degrees F.
Beautiful day. bright sun- 60 degrees at 10 a.m. water temp 50 degrees. 1pair of loons- 6 boats on lake.
Overcast and windy. no sun. water temp. 59 degrees.
Clear day- slight chop on water. lots of aquatic plants- water temp 63 degrees.
Clear day- lots of puffy clouds. hard to see without sun. water temp 65 degrees F.
Partly cloudy- air 80 degrees F.- water 71 degrees F. brownish water. 3.5" rain in last 3 days.
Mostly cloudy- water temp 74 degrees F. lake in bloom. slight chop on water.
Scattered clouds- water 71 degrees F.- air 80 degrees F. beautiful day- north wind.
Bright sunny day- no wind. water 70 degrees- air 80 degrees F.
Cloudy- light drizzle. water temp 66 degrees F.
Lots of weeds floating on lake. milfoil terrible. water 56 degrees- air 60 degrees F.
Sunshine- lots of wind. air 70 degrees- water 50 degrees.
Milfoil all over lake. up to top of water. water dangerously low "yuck".

Christine Goff assisted.  Partly sunny day with a very strong wind from the S.W.  Ambient air temperature was 78 F.   Many eagles and loons seen

My wife Christine assisted.   Mostly cloudy day with a relatively strong wind from the north.  Ambient air temperature was 62 F.  Milfoil is currently breaking the surface in some isolated areas.  Submerged Milfoil is seen in other areas.  Lake level is normal.   Water color is green and our preception rated at #2.  Plenty of eagles flying about.  Several pairs of loons were seen.
Sunny.  Moderate breeze from SW.   Ambient temperature was 68 degrees F.  Cloud cover at about 10%.  Numerous eagles and loons observed.
81 degrees. Slight breeze from NW.  Very sunny.
Sunny.  Virtually flat lake with no breeze.
Sunny day.  Slight breeze from southwest.
72 degrees F. ambient temperature. Slight breeze from west. Very sunny.

Relatively strong breeze/wave action from NW.  Completely overcast with slight mist. 54 degrees ambient air temp.  Loons and lake gulls present.  Eagles not to be seen.  Certainly not a day to spend at the beach.
Overcast sky.  Light breeze from east.  45 degrees F ambient temperature.
Sunny day.  Light to no breeze.
Sunny day.  Light breeze from SE.  Minimal wave movement. 83 degrees Fahrenheit ambient air temperature.
Ambient air temp was 77 degrees.  Gusty wind from W/SW with moderate chop in immediate area of sampling.  Sunny with high hazy cloud civer.
Air temp was 48 degrees Fahrenheit- with a slight breeze from the SE.  Lightly clouded sky.
No wind.  Mostly sunny.  Ambient air temp was 63 degrees F.  High lake level.
83 degrees ambient air temp.  Sunny with little wave action
Water temp = 69.7. Skies clear. 6 in chop.
Ambient air temp was 64 degrees F.  Light breeze from the SE.  Slight wave action.  Clear sky.
69 degrees air temp; sunny; virtually no wind; no waves
70 deg. F. air temp- Sunny- light wind ~ 3 mph from ENE.  Dick Groff also present for sampling.
Air temp 83 deg F- Sunny- light NW wind at ~ 3 mph.
73 degrees- calm wind- and mostly sunny
2.75 inches of rain last night. 5" chop.
8 inch chop- hazy sun- water temp 79 degrees F
